data.description: Welcome to 8203 Half Dome Court, a luxurious haven nestled in the sought-after community of Canyon Trails. This exquisite 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home embodies elegance and comfort, offering a lifestyle of both relaxation and entertainment. The first floor features a bedroom and full bath. The 2nd level primary suite has two walk-in closets, an en-suite with dual vanities, and a separate tub and shower. Updated dine-in kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances and 42'' cabinets. Porcelain tile throughout and custom lighting. The backyard has a screened lanai and plenty of room for a pool! The community offers Basketball, Volleyball, a Arcade, Water Park with Wading Pool and Spray Stations, Social Hall, Fitness Center, Resort Style Pool, and Tennis. Don't miss out!
